The App may display advertisements provided by third‑party ad networks. These ad networks may collect data about your device and usage to deliver ads and measure performance. Data collected may include device identifiers and advertising identifiers. Ad networks may also combine information collected from your use of the App with other information they have.

If you are in a jurisdiction requiring consent for personalized advertising (for example, EEA), we will surface a consent prompt when necessary. You can opt out of interest‑based advertising via your device settings (Google Ad Settings on Android) or by using the platform privacy controls.

